K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-018:166a-0: @166a *// yang ni sbyor ba'i las rnams ni //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-018:166a-1: dgos pa chen po 'di gsungs so //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-018:166a-2: tshogs kyi bdag po'i sku tsandan na nam rin po che las byas te rab gnas byas la mchod pa phul te /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-018:166a-15: ser ba ji tsam 'dod pa'i dbyibs che chung byas la khrag gi byugs la bdun dang bdun phrag mang du byas te ka ka ki ku'i thod pa'i nang du blugs te sprin gyis dgab par bya'o //
K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-018:166a-16: ka ka'i thod pa la sngags bri bar bya'o //

K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-018:166b-1: brum brum bha ri sha ya zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i sngags 'bum phrag gcig bzlas pa dang /

K12acip-k_lha_sa-091-018:167a-4: tshogs kyi bdag po'i rgyud dngos grub 'byung ba zhes bya ba rdzogs so ////
